OL,3,CHillsborough Law delayed over security
OL,4,Cservices concerns
OL,6,FThe next stage of the landmark
OL,7,FHillsborough Law in Parliament will be
OL,8,Fdelayed after concerns were raised
OL,9,Fthat the "duty of candour" is being
OL,10,Fwatered down for security services
OL,11,Flike MI5 and MI6.
OL,13,FThe Public Office Accountability Bill
OL,14,Fwould mean public servants could face
OL,15,Fjail if they are found not to have
OL,16,Ftold the truth during investigations
OL,17,For inquiries.
