OL,3,CHillsborough Law delayed over security
OL,4,Cservices concerns
OL,6,FIt follows the Hillsborough Disaster
OL,7,Fin 1989, which saw 97 football fans
OL,8,Funlawfully killed in a crush at the FA
OL,9,FCup semi-final, and subsequent efforts
OL,10,Fby some officials to mislead about
OL,11,Fevents that led up to the tragedy.
OL,13,FThe bill was due to pass a key stage -
OL,14,Fthe Report Stage - in the House of
OL,15,FCommons on Wednesday 14 January, but
OL,16,Fthis has now been delayed over
OL,17,Fconcerns of how the intelligence
OL,18,Fservices will be covered by the law.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
