OL,3,CHillsborough Law delayed over security
OL,4,Cservices concerns
OL,6,FHillsborough campaigners and
OL,7,FManchester Arena families are expected
OL,8,Fto meet the prime minister at Downing
OL,9,FStreet to discuss the government's
OL,10,Fmoves on this area, which they
OL,11,Fdescribe as "a carve out that we
OL,12,Fcannot accept".
OL,14,FThey say they will warn the government
OL,15,Fagainst breaking its promises by
OL,16,F"introducing loopholes" for the
OL,17,Fsecurity services, insisting that no
OL,18,Fpublic authority should be exempt from
OL,19,Fthe legislation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
