OL,3,CHillsborough Law delayed over security
OL,4,Cservices concerns
OL,6,F"This latest delay is welcome, but
OL,7,Fonly if it is used to fix what is now
OL,8,Fwrong. Families cannot accept a law
OL,9,Fthat allows the heads of the security
OL,10,Fservices to hide serious failures
OL,11,Fbehind a vague claim of national
OL,12,Fsecurity."
OL,14,FFamilies who lost loved ones in the
OL,15,FManchester Arena bombing recently
OL,16,Fwrote to the Prime Minister calling on
OL,17,Fhim to ensure the new law will apply
OL,18,Fin the fullest way to security
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
