OL,3,CHillsborough Law delayed over security
OL,4,Cservices concerns
OL,6,F"MI5, MI6 and GCHQ are as high up the
OL,7,Fchain as you can get so why would any
OL,8,Fother service feel they needed to tell
OL,9,Fthe truth when those at the top are
OL,10,Fexempt? Lead by example is what we've
OL,11,Falways believed."
OL,13,FThe passage of the landmark
OL,14,FHillsborough Law is expected to be
OL,15,Fdelayed until 19 January.
